      <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-brand-200 bg-brand-50 p-6">
  <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-900 mb-3">What I’m known for</h3>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
    <li>8+ years shipping high-traffic mobile products (including PayPay).</li>
    <li>AI, computer vision, and NLP research & production engineering.</li>
    <li>Clean architectures, testing discipline, CI/CD, and pragmatic delivery.</li>
  </ul>
</div>


